    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/79"
                            >Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/72"
                            >Lotharius</persName> divina providente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Regalem decet excellentiam subditis sibi
                        fidelibus gratuiti [mu]neris dona prebere. Quocirca omnium sibi fidelium
                        sanctae Dei Ecclesie nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum devotio noverit,
                        qualiter <rs key="#Intercessory">interventu ac petitione</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Count #fidelisOf"><name ref="Ingelbertus"
                                >Ingelberti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> dilectique <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs>
                        nostri per hoc nostrum pre[ceptu]m, prout iuste et legaliter possumus,
                        confirmamus ac corroboramus, concedimus, donamus atque largimur <persName
                            key="#fidelisOf"><name ref="Richardus">Richardo</name></persName> cuidam
                        nostro <rs key="#fidelisOf">fideli</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansos tres</rs> positos in <placeName ref="#places/2791"
                            >valle [Oxil]a</placeName>, in <rs key="#Villas">villa</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Villas #Mansi #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/2399">Aureliaco</geogName>, sicut quondam fueru[n]t
                        possessi a <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/93">Gariardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comite</rs> de <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/521">Fontaneto</placeName>, una cum
                            <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis</rs> inibi residentibus, quorum nomina
                        sunt: <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Custo"
                        >Custo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Hilarius"
                                >Hilarius</name></persName>, <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominicus</name></persName>, reliquisque <rs
                            key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs> ad ipsas res et <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">massaritia</rs> pertinentibus; verum
                        etiam cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">pascuis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscariis</rs>, <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>, <rs key="#Natural_landscape"
                            >vallibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains">alpibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Natural_landscape">planitiebus</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis
                            aquarumve decursibus</rs> et cum omnibus que dici vel nominari possunt
                        ad ipsas res et <rs key="#Mansi">mansos</rs> aspitientibus in integrum, ut
                        habeat, teneat firmiterque possideat ipse suique heredes habeantque
                        potestatem tenendi, donandi, vendendi, commutandi, alienandi, pro anima
                        iudicandi, vel quicquid eorum decreverit animus faciendi, omnium hominum
                        controversia remota. Si quis igitur huius nostri precepti confirmationem seu
                        largitionem aliquando infringere conatus fuerit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras quinquaginti</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem kamere nostre</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem prefato Richardo
                            suisque heredibus</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur diligentiusque ab
                        omnibus observetur, manibus propriis roborantes anulo nostro insigniri
                        iussimus. Signa serenissimorum (M F) (M F) Hugonis et Lotharii regum.
                            <persName key="#Chaplain #Deacons"><name ref="Theodulfus"
                                >Teodulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> et <rs key="#Chaplain">regius
                            capellanus</rs> regio iussu recognovi et subscripsi (S R) (SI D). Data
                        IIII nonas martii, anno dominice incarnationis DCCCCXLV, regni vero domni
                        Hugonis XVIIII, Lotharii XIIII, indictione tertia. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName>. feliciter, AMEN. </ab>
